#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/containers/podman-nextcloud.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "    Podman is tool for managing containers, specifically OCI (Open Containers Initiative) containers. It's designed to be pretty much Docker-compatible, in that most if not all of the same commands will work for both tools. If \"Docker\" means nothing to you—or even if you're just curious—you can read more about Podman and how it works on [Podman's own website](https://podman.io).\n"
